name: Delta Variant every 8PM-4AM in the Philippines
description:
Delta Variant every 8PM-4AM in the Philippines by Jarrett Cross | 2021 | VQGAN + CLIP, Photomanipulation, Graphic Design. 

Delta Variant is treated like a monster here in the Philippines. A monster they think would need military force in order to be eradicated. Humongous metal tanks are found on the streets; policemen with high caliber weapons wander around waiting for their own trigger happy moment against the Delta Variant. Like WTF?! R u serious?! Do you think shooting the virus will save everyone in the world from it?! 

Framed like an old movie poster cos it's a fkng shtshw! 

I hope this ends soonest! I hope all is well with you too and your family and friends. Always take care. 

Genesis piece of the Journal of Jarrett Cross.

Journal of Jarrett Cross was conceptualised and was started during the Delta Variant Enhanced Community Quarantine Season 3 in Manila, Philippines. 

#HEN200k
